Helper scripts for setting up the dotfiles and git config.

The setup_links.py script just makes it easy to setup the symlinks while
setup_git.sh automates git configurations I always seem to forget :)

Run setup to run the above scripts and also initialize git submodules

To change the shell for the current user, run
    chsh -s /bin/zsh

Fix the brightness controls after installing nvidia drivers by copying the xorg file
